  "description": "<div id=\"product-detail\" style=\"font-family:Arial; font-size:16px; line-height:1.6;\">\n\n    <h4>Application:</h4>\n    <p>Compatible with 2007-2022 Jeep Wrangler (JK &amp; JL) with 1-2.5\" lift</p>\n\n    <h4>Features:</h4>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Eye-to-eye length: 11 in (280 mm); Full length: 12.5 in (317 mm)</li>\n        <li>Easy installation: Direct replacement of the original part</li>\n        <li>Package includes: 2 pieces of rear sway bar links</li>\n        <li>No greasing needed</li>\n        <li>100% brand new items, never used or installed</li>\n        <li>Accessories shown in the photos are included</li>\n        <li>1-year warranty for any manufacturing defect</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h4>Sway Bar Benefit:</h4>\n    <p>\n        Helps to stabilize the body of the vehicle relative to the suspension. It is fixed on two chassis guide rails and is connected to the axle housing through the connecting rod at the end of the beam. \n        The spring steel structure of the sway bar acts like a torsion bar and resists body roll when turning.\n    </p>\n\n</div>\n",
